[Nick notes]:

 - the adaptive value of feelings and emotions
 - The cost of numbing ourselves
 - Pain is always an adaptive signal. Painful emotions are adaptive
 - Self soothing and self awareness
 - Emotional intelligence
 - acknoledging and processing emotions and feelings instead of brushing them off
 - Unresolved feelings and emotions create a state of dis-ease
 - Determining when emotions are no longer serving us well

 - harms of ignoring emotions
 - A curiosity to engage with the process of understanding feelings and emotions
 - all emotions are valuable, some are useful
 - emotional assessment: what am I feeling? why am I feeling it? How long do I want to feel this way for? Is this feeling serving me well?


